{
  "stem": "12494.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A-- how would you say that in English-- someone who belonged to the German minority in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Who, as a result of that, of course, was expected to have the German mother language and who fell on the Eastern Front.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And since I spoke German, my mother and I were East German, and I had his papers, everything checked out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When they stopped me, and they check back with the police, is so and so indeed so and so, they-- it-- it would-- it would check out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So you had all degrees of-- of-- all degrees-- excellent papers and bad papers and all the degrees in between.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never was in danger of being arrested.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was many times called upon to identify myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, if you call that a-- you know, each of those events are events when your heart is beating in your throat, what will happen now.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I never was caught.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I-- I had very good papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were always honored, and I never had a problem.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only time I had a problem was when I hailed a taxi, on one occasion.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At that time, taxis-- taxis were hailed on the basis of several people sharing them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There weren't enough taxis in Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I hailed a taxi.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I had to get back home before the deadline of whatever hour it was when I have to be home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I had my raincoat [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on my arm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The raincoat had a star on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The jacket in which was had no star.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I had to change from non-Jew to Jew before getting home.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
